Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 07 of Hip MRI
When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then Finding dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Bursitis' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Right' radio button is enabled
And 'Left' radio button is enabled

And 'Trochanteric bursa' radio button is enabled
And 'Iliopectineal bursa' radio button is enabled
And 'Iliopsoas bursa' radio button is enabled
And 'Ischial bursa' radio button is enabled
And 'Obturator externus bursa' radio button is enabled
And 'Quadratus femoris bursa' radio button is enabled
And 'Subgluteal bursa' radio button is enabled

And 'lll defined' radio button is enabled
And 'Sharp' radio button is enabled

And 'Max. diameter bursa' input field is enabled

And 'Hemorrhage' checkbox is enabled
And 'Calcifications' checkbox is enabled

And 'Perifocal soft tissue edema' checkbox is enabled
And 'Septic bursitis' checkbox is enabled
And 'Abscess' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ruptured bursa' checkbox is enabled
And 'Secondary osteomyelitis' checkbox is enabled
